<div3 type="death" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head>Died,</head> 
<div4 type="obit" n="1" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head /> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="512" /> On the <dateStruct value="--24" full="yes" authname="---24"><day reg="24" full="yes">24th inst.</day></dateStruct>, after a severe illness of <measure n="2months" type="date">two months</measure>, <persName n="Wesley,,John,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00363" reg="default:Wesley,John,,," authname="wesley,john"><foreName full="yes">John</foreName> <surname full="yes">Wesley</surname></persName>, only child of <persName><foreName full="yes">William</foreName></persName> J and <persName n="Ostrander,,Ann,E.,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00364" reg="default:Ostrander,Ann,E.,," authname="ostrander,ann,e."><foreName full="yes">Ann</foreName> <foreName full="yes">E.</foreName> <surname full="yes">Ostrander</surname></persName>, aged <num value="1">1</num> year <measure n="11months" type="date">11 months</measure> and <measure n="24days" type="date">24 days</measure>. </p> 
<div5 type="poem" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head /> <lg type="stanza" org="uniform" sample="complete"> <l><hi rend="smallcaps"><persName><foreName full="yes">Wesley</foreName></persName></hi> came a while on earth to smile, </l><l>Then sweetly passed away, </l><l>Like early flowers in summer bowers, </l><l>That blossom in <dateStruct value="-05-" full="yes" authname="--05"><month reg="05" full="yes">May</month></dateStruct>, </l> </lg> <lg type="stanza" org="uniform" sample="complete"> <l>But ch?

<milestone unit="sentence" n="513" />no more his spirit pure </l><l>Can bloom on earth again-- </l><l>The little dove has down above </l><l>To sing another sirain, </l> </lg> <lg type="stanza" org="uniform" sample="complete"> <l>Though over his tomb in silent gloom </l><l>We are a burning tear, </l><l><hi rend="smallcaps"><persName><foreName full="yes">Wesley</foreName></persName>'s</hi> blest and is at rett.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="514" /></l><l>While we are mourn are here.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="515" /></l> </lg> 
<p> The funeral will take place from the <rs>Oregon Hill</rs> <orgName n="Baptist Church" type="church">Baptist Church</orgName>, this morning, at <time value="11oclock">11 o'clock</time>. The friends and acquaintances of the family are respectfully invited to attend. </p> </div5> </div4> 
<div4 type="obit" n="2" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head /> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="516" /> On <dateStruct full="yes"><day type="name" full="yes">Wednesday</day></dateStruct>, <num value="24" type="ordinal">24th</num> inst, at <time value="12pm">12 o'clock P. M.</time>, <persName n="Samuel,,Richard,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00365" reg="default:Samuel,Richard,,," authname="samuel,richard"><foreName full="yes">Richard</foreName> <surname full="yes">Samuel</surname></persName>, infant son of <persName><foreName full="yes">John</foreName></persName> D. <unclear /> <persName n="Schwalmeyer,,Wilimenor,C.,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00366" reg="default:Schwalmeyer,Wilimenor,C.,," authname="schwalmeyer,wilimenor,c."><foreName full="yes">Wilimenor</foreName> <foreName full="yes">C.</foreName> <surname full="yes">Schwalmeyer</surname></persName>, aged <num value="1">1</num> year <measure n="10months" type="date">10 months</measure> and <measure n="15days" type="date">15 days</measure>. </p> 
<div5 type="poem" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head /> <lg type="stanza" org="uniform" sample="complete"> <l>Rejoice for a son deceased, </l><l>Our loss is his <unclear /> gain-- </l><l>A soul out of prison released, </l><l>And freed from his bodily pals.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="517" /></l> </lg> <lg type="stanza" org="uniform" sample="complete"> <l>With gouge let us follow his night, </l><l>And <unclear>unt</unclear> with his spirit above-- </l><l>Escaped to the manstens of light.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="518" /></l><l>And lodred in the <name>Edes</name> of love.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="519" /></l> </lg> 
<p> On the <dateStruct value="--26" full="yes" authname="---26"><day reg="26" full="yes">26th inst.</day></dateStruct>, <persName n="Folkes,Mrs.,Ann,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00367" reg="default:Folkes,Ann,,," authname="folkes,ann"><roleName n="Mrs." full="yes">Mrs.</roleName> <foreName full="yes">Ann</foreName> <surname full="yes">Folkes</surname></persName>, in the <num value="71" type="ordinal">71st</num> year of her age. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="520" /> Her funeral with take place this afternoon at <num value="4">4</num> ¼ o'clock, from <address><street n="Clay Street">Clay Street</street></address> <orgName n="Methodist Church" type="church">Methodist Church</orgName>--The friends of the family are invited to attend. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="521" /> As the residence of <persName n="Forgussen,,A.,M.,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00368" reg="default:Forgussen,A.,M.,," authname="forgussen,a.,m."><foreName full="yes">A.</foreName> <foreName full="yes">M.</foreName> <surname full="yes">Forgussen</surname></persName>, <placeName reg="Charles City, Virginia, United States" key="tgn,1002257" authname="tgn,1002257">Charles City county</placeName>, on the <date value="07-29" authname="--07-29">29th July, </date> <persName n="Tare,,Maria,P.,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00369" reg="default:Tare,Maria,P.,," authname="tare,maria,p."><foreName full="yes">Maria</foreName> <foreName full="yes">P.</foreName> <surname full="yes">Tare</surname></persName>, daughter of <persName n="Tabn,,John,F.,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00370" reg="default:Tabn,John,F.,," authname="tabn,john,f."><foreName full="yes">John</foreName> <foreName full="yes">F.</foreName> <surname full="yes">Tabn</surname></persName>, of <placeName reg="Richmond, Richmond, Virginia" key="tgn,7013964" authname="tgn,7013964">Richmond</placeName>, aged months and <measure n="24days" type="date">24 days</measure>. </p> </div5> </div4> </div3> </div2> 
