<div2 type="announcement" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head /> 
<div3 type="orders" n="1" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head>Volunteers, attentions.</head> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="810" /> The undersigned, <num value="2">two</num> of whom have been for some time members of volunteer companies, the other a Lieutenant of the <orgName n="Provisional Army" type="misc">Provisional Army of <placeName reg="Virginia, United States, North and Central America" key="tgn,7007919" authname="tgn,7007919">Virginia</placeName></orgName>, are desirous of raising an infantry Company, to be styled the <q direct="unspecified">"<persName n="Southerns,,Richmond,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00576" reg="default:Southerns,Richmond,,," authname="southerns,richmond"><foreName full="yes">Richmond</foreName> <surname full="yes">Southerns</surname></persName>."</q> </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="811" /> Uniforms and Accountrements free. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="812" /> Those wishing to go promptly into service, will call at the <name>Rendezvous</name> on <address><street n="Wall street">Wall street</street></address>, over the <q direct="unspecified">"City Arms,"</q> opposite the <rs type="place">St. Charles Hotel</rs>, and enrol their names. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="813" /> Come quickly, and let us at once to the field. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="814" /> <persName n="Meredith,,Bernard,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00577" reg="default:Meredith,Bernard,,," authname="meredith,bernard"><foreName full="yes">Bernard</foreName> <surname full="yes">Meredith</surname></persName>,<lb />Corner <address><street n="Grace Street">Grace</street></address> and <address><street n="7 Street">7th sts.</street></address><lb /><persName n="Pickett,,Charles,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00578" reg="default:Pickett,Charles,,," authname="pickett,charles"><foreName n="Charles" full="yes">Chas.</foreName> <surname full="yes">Pickett</surname></persName>,<lb />Corner <address><street n="Leigh Street">Leigh</street></address> and <address><street n="6 Street">6th sts.</street></address><lb /><persName n="Wadsworth,,John,S.,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00579" reg="default:Wadsworth,John,S.,," authname="wadsworth,john,s."><foreName full="yes">John</foreName> <foreName full="yes">S.</foreName> <surname full="yes">Wadsworth</surname></persName>, </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="815" /> jy <num value="26">26</num>--ts <address><street n="Pearl Street 16">No. 16 Pearl street</street></address>. </p> </div3> </div2> 
