<div1 type="news" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head /> 
<div2 type="telegraphic" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head>Telegraphic News.<lb />reported for the <orgName n="Richmond Dispatch" type="newspaper">Richmond Dispatch</orgName>.</head> 
<div3 type="letter" n="1" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head>[special Dispatch to the <orgName n="Richmond Dispatch" type="newspaper">Richmond Dispatch</orgName>.]<lb /><persName n="Jackson,Governor,,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00580" reg="nearbymention:Jackson,Claiborne,F.,," authname="jackson,claiborne,f."><roleName n="Governor" full="yes">Governor</roleName> <surname full="yes">Jackson</surname></persName> in <placeName reg="Knoxville, Knox, Tennessee" key="tgn,7013841" authname="tgn,7013841">Knoxville</placeName> — the recent victory.</head> <opener> <dateline> <name type="place">Knoxville, Tenn.,</name> <date value="07-25" authname="--07-25">July 25.</date> </dateline> </opener> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="817" /> <hi rend="smallcaps"><placeName reg="Knoxville, Knox, Tennessee" key="tgn,7013841" authname="tgn,7013841">Knoxville</placeName>,</hi> <dateStruct value="-07-25" full="yes" authname="--07-25"><month reg="07" full="yes">July</month> <day reg="25" full="yes">25</day></dateStruct>. --<persName n="Jackson,Governor,,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00581" reg="nearbymention:Jackson,Claiborne,F.,," authname="jackson,claiborne,f."><roleName n="Governor" full="yes">Governor</roleName> <surname full="yes">Jackson</surname></persName> and <persName n="Atkinson,General,,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00582" reg="nearbymention:Atkinson,J.,Anthony,," authname="atkinson,j.,anthony"><roleName n="General" full="yes">General</roleName> <surname full="yes">Atkinson</surname></persName>, of <placeName reg="Missouri" key="tgn,7007523" authname="tgn,7007523">Missouri</placeName>, passed through to-day on their way to <placeName reg="Richmond, Richmond, Virginia" key="tgn,7013964" authname="tgn,7013964">Richmond</placeName>.--Both made speeches, and told of wrongs that made our blood boil within us. The Governor is exiled from his State.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="818" />He says <num value="200000">two hundred thousand</num> troops are ready to defend her cause if they had arms. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="819" /> The news of the victory at <placeName key="tgn,2112877" n="1.000 541" reg="manassas, manassas, virginia" authname="tgn,2112877">Manassas</placeName> was received here with great enthusiasm — bell rung.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="820" />cannon fired, and fire-works in the evening.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="821" />Very good for <placeName reg="Knoxville, Knox, Tennessee" key="tgn,7013841" authname="tgn,7013841">Knoxville</placeName>. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="822" /> Troops from everywhere are now pouring over these railroads.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="823" />Can hardly get transportation.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="824" />All are the right kind of men.--No truth in the story of <persName n="McCulloch,,,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00583" reg="mostcommon:McCulloch,Ben,,,:1" authname="mcculloch,ben"><surname full="yes">McCulloch</surname></persName>'s and <placeName reg="Jackson, Madison, Tennessee" key="tgn,2099733" authname="tgn,2099733">Jackson</placeName>'s quarreling. </p> <closer> <signed><orgName type="college" n="Columbian college">Columbian</orgName>.</signed> </closer> </div3> 
<div3 type="letter" n="2" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head>Various War Matters.</head> <opener> <dateline> <name type="place">Washington,</name> <date value="07-25" authname="--07-25">July 25.</date> </dateline> </opener> 
<p rend="nobreak">

<milestone unit="sentence" n="825" /> --The Federal pickets at <placeName><placeName key="tgn,2111722" n="1.000 6" reg="falls church, falls church, virginia" authname="tgn,2111722">Fall's Church</placeName> (<distance reg="4miles" full="yes" exact="U">four miles</distance></placeName> from <placeName reg="Alexandria, Alexandria, Virginia" key="tgn,7013269" authname="tgn,7013269">Alexandria</placeName>,) were driven in early on <dateStruct full="yes"><day type="name" full="yes">Wednesday</day></dateStruct>. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="826" /> <persName n="McClellan,General,,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00584" reg="nearbymention:McClellan,George,B.,," authname="mcclellan,george,b."><roleName n="General" full="yes">Gen.</roleName> <surname full="yes">McClellan</surname></persName> arrived here to-day. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="827" /> The <orgName n="War Department" type="department">War Department</orgName> is engaged in a thorough reorganization of the <orgName n="Army" type="military">Army</orgName>.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="828" />The old system will be changed, and reliable officers will be provided, subject to an examination of a <orgName n="Officers Board" type="board">Board of Officers</orgName> appointed by the <orgName n="War Department" type="department">War Department</orgName>. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="829" /> <num value="2">Two</num> gentlemen, both by the name of <persName n="Bradley,,,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00585" reg="mostcommon:Bradley,nomatch:0" authname="bradley"><surname full="yes">Bradley</surname></persName>, <num value="1">one</num> of them a student in the ministry, have been arrested at <placeName reg="Alexandria, Alexandria, Virginia" key="tgn,7013269" authname="tgn,7013269">Alexandria</placeName>. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="830" /> <placeName key="tgn,2112877" n="1.000 541" reg="manassas, manassas, virginia" authname="tgn,2112877">Manassas</placeName> spied and the <rs>Federal</rs> pickets have been withdrawn to within <placeName><distance reg="2miles" full="yes" exact="U">two miles</distance> of <placeName reg="Alexandria, Alexandria, Virginia" key="tgn,7013269" authname="tgn,7013269">Alexandria</placeName></placeName>. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="831" /> It is reported that <num value="80000">eighty thousand</num> volunteers throughout the <rs>North</rs> have been accepted by the <orgName n="War Department" type="department">War Department</orgName>.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="832" />(This is only reported.) </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="833" /> <placeName reg="France" key="tgn,1000070" authname="tgn,1000070">France</placeName> and <placeName reg="United Kingdom" key="tgn,7002445" authname="tgn,7002445">England</placeName> are undoubtedly discussing the blockade, with a view of making propositions. </p> </div3> 
<div3 type="letter" n="3" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head>Visit to <placeName reg="Richmond, Richmond, Virginia" key="tgn,7013964" authname="tgn,7013964">Richmond</placeName> postponed — competent officers Wanted, &amp;c.</head> <opener> <dateline> <name type="place">New York,</name> <date value="07-24" authname="--07-24">July 24.</date> </dateline> </opener> 
<p rend="nobreak">

<milestone unit="sentence" n="834" /> --The <placeName reg="Washington, District of Columbia, United States" key="tgn,7013962" authname="tgn,7013962">Washington</placeName> correspondent of the <hi rend="italics">Herald,</hi> of this morning, says the disasters of Sunday have thrown the <rs>Government</rs> back to the defences occupied <measure n="3months" type="date">three months</measure> ago. Offensive operations will not be commenced before fall.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="835" />[Probably not, if then.] </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="836" /> All department letters since the defeat contain the following: <cit><q rend="inline" direct="unspecified">"Your regiment is accepted with the distinct understanding that this department will revoke the commissions of all officers who prove incompetent to command."</q><bibl default="NO" /></cit> </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="837" /> The special correspondent of the <rs>Herald</rs> reports a large encampment of the <rs>Confederates</rs> between <persName n="Fairfax,,,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00586" reg="mostcommon:Fairfax,nomatch:0" authname="fairfax"><surname full="yes">Fairfax</surname></persName> and <placeName reg="Centreville, Fairfax, Virginia" key="tgn,2111026" authname="tgn,2111026">Centreville</placeName>. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="838" /> <persName n="Bartlett,Colonel,,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00587" reg="mostcommon:Bartlett,nomatch:0" authname="bartlett"><roleName n="Colonel" full="yes">Col.</roleName> <surname full="yes">Bartlett</surname></persName>, of the <orgName type="mil" key="MSRegiment">Mississippi Regiment</orgName>, has been brought a prisoner to <placeName reg="Washington, District of Columbia, United States" key="tgn,7013962" authname="tgn,7013962">Washington</placeName>. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="839" /> <num value="2">Two</num> <placeName key="tgn,7012924" n="1.000 259" reg="indianapolis, marion, indiana" authname="tgn,7012924">Indianapolis</placeName> regiments have returned from <placeName reg="Virginia, United States, North and Central America" key="tgn,7007919" authname="tgn,7007919">Virginia</placeName> and mustered out of the service.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="840" /><num value="3">Three</num> more are on their way home.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="841" />[And more <q direct="unspecified">"want to go home,"</q> doubtless.] </p> </div3> 
<div3 type="letter" n="4" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head>Arrest — Preparations for defence — <persName n="Lincoln,,,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00588" reg="mostcommon:Lincoln,nomatch:0" authname="lincoln"><surname full="yes">Lincoln</surname></persName> and the remnant of the <num value="69" type="ordinal">69th</num>.</head> <opener> <dateline> <name type="place">Washington,</name> <date value="07-23" authname="--07-23">July 23.</date> </dateline> </opener> 
<p rend="nobreak">

<milestone unit="sentence" n="842" /> --<persName n="Bell,Doctor,,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00589" reg="mostcommon:Bell,nomatch:0" authname="bell"><roleName n="Doctor" full="yes">Dr.</roleName> <surname full="yes">Bell</surname></persName> has been arrested for uttering treasonable sentiments.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="843" />He was saved from the mob by the interference of officers. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="844" /> The Federals are throwing up entrenchments at <placeName reg="Centreville, Fairfax, Virginia" key="tgn,2111026" authname="tgn,2111026">Centreville</placeName>. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="845" /> <placeName reg="The President">The President</placeName> and <persName n="Seward,Secretary,,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00590" reg="mostcommon:Seward,nomatch:0" authname="seward"><roleName n="Secretary" full="yes">Secretary</roleName> <surname full="yes">Seward</surname></persName> visited the <rs>Virginia</rs> side of the <rs>Potomac</rs> to day. <placeName reg="The President">The President</placeName> complimented the <orgName type="regiment" key="69NYRegiment">69th New York Regiment</orgName>, and urged them to re-enlist.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="846" />They reported, they would if the <rs>President</rs> desired it. <persName n="Lincoln,,,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00591" reg="mostcommon:Lincoln,nomatch:0" authname="lincoln"><surname full="yes">Lincoln</surname></persName> replied, <q direct="unspecified">"Then I do desire that the whole regiment shall re-enlist."</q> He gave a complimentary letter to the regiment. </p> </div3> 
<div3 type="letter" n="5" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head>The War in <placeName reg="Missouri" key="tgn,7007523" authname="tgn,7007523">Missouri</placeName>.</head> <opener> <dateline> <name type="place">St. Louis,</name> <date value="07-23" authname="--07-23">July 23.</date> </dateline> </opener> 
<p rend="nobreak">

<milestone unit="sentence" n="847" /> --A large body of Missourians are marching from <persName n="Smith,,,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00592" reg="nearbymention:Smith,Kirby,,," authname="smith,kirby"><surname full="yes">Smith</surname></persName>, in <placeName reg="Missouri" key="tgn,7007523" authname="tgn,7007523"><rs type="direction">East</rs> Missouri</placeName>, on <placeName key="tgn,7021890" n="1.000 1" reg="Pilot Knob, Iron, Missouri" authname="tgn,7021890">Pilot Knob</placeName>, the <rs>Southern</rs> termini of the <orgName n="Iron Mountain Railroad" type="railroad">Iron Mountain Railroad</orgName>. <persName n="Bland,General,,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00593" reg="mostcommon:Bland,nomatch:0" authname="bland"><roleName n="General" full="yes">General</roleName> <surname full="yes">Bland</surname></persName>, a Federal commander, is stationed there, and has issued a call for reinforcements immediately. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="848" /> <num value="4">Four</num> men were recently shot at <placeName reg="Great Meadows, Warren, New Jersey" key="tgn,2064855" authname="tgn,2064855">Denville</placeName>, Mo., by the <rs>Federals</rs>, for hanging <persName n="Sharp,Colonel,,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00594" reg="mostcommon:Sharp,nomatch:0" authname="sharp"><roleName n="Colonel" full="yes">Col.</roleName> <surname full="yes">Sharp</surname></persName> and <persName n="Jaiger,Lieutenant,,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00595" reg="mostcommon:Jaiger,nomatch:0" authname="jaiger"><roleName n="Lieutenant" full="yes">Lieut.</roleName> <surname full="yes">Jaiger</surname></persName>. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="849" /> <persName n="Zeigle,General,,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00596" reg="mostcommon:Zeigle,nomatch:0" authname="zeigle"><roleName n="General" full="yes">General</roleName> <surname full="yes">Zeigle</surname></persName> was at <placeName reg="Springfield, Greene, Missouri" key="tgn,7014532" authname="tgn,7014532">Springfield</placeName> with <num value="8000">8,000</num> men, and organizing a command for <measure n="3years" type="date">3 years</measure> service. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="850" /> <persName n="McCulloch,General,Ben,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00597" reg="default:McCulloch,Ben,,," authname="mcculloch,ben"><roleName n="General" full="yes">General</roleName> <foreName full="yes">Ben</foreName> <surname full="yes">McCulloch</surname></persName> was at <placeName reg="Camp Walker">Camp Walker</placeName>, in <placeName reg="Arkansas, United States, North and Central America" key="tgn,7016172" authname="tgn,7016172">Arkansas</placeName>, with <num value="5000">5,000</num> men well armed. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="851" /> <persName n="Jackson,Governor,,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00598" reg="nearbymention:Jackson,Claiborne,F.,," authname="jackson,claiborne,f."><roleName n="Governor" full="yes">Gov.</roleName> <surname full="yes">Jackson</surname></persName> was near <persName n="McCulloch,,,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00599" reg="nearbymention:McCulloch,Ben,,," authname="mcculloch,ben"><surname full="yes">McCulloch</surname></persName> with <num value="10000">10,000</num> men. </p> </div3> 
<div3 type="letter" n="6" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head>Federal Assertions — troops tendered.</head> <opener> <dateline> <name type="place">Washington,</name> <date value="07-24" authname="--07-24">July 24.</date> </dateline> </opener> 
<p rend="nobreak">

<milestone unit="sentence" n="852" /> --The business at the <orgName n="War Department" type="department">War Department</orgName> is very heavy. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="853" /> Telegraphic messages are accumulating, and all tendering troops. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="854" /> <placeName reg="Illinois" key="tgn,7007251" authname="tgn,7007251">Illinois</placeName> has offered <num value="17">seventeen</num>, and <placeName reg="Indiana" key="tgn,7007252" authname="tgn,7007252">Indiana</placeName> <num value="10">ten</num> regiments. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="855" /> The wounded at the <rs n="Battle of Bull Run" type="battle">battle of Bull's Run</rs> continue to arrive. </p> </div3> 
<div3 type="letter" n="7" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head><placeName reg="Missouri" key="tgn,7007523" authname="tgn,7007523">Missouri</placeName> <orgName n="State Convention" type="convention">State Convention</orgName>.</head> <opener> <dateline> <name type="place">Jefferson City, Mo.,</name> <date value="07-24" authname="--07-24">July 24.</date> </dateline> </opener> 
<p rend="nobreak">

<milestone unit="sentence" n="856" /> --In the <rs>Convention</rs>, on yesterday, a resolution was offered to the effect that any change in the <orgName n="Department of the Executive" type="government">Executive Department</orgName> or State Government will not promote the welfare of <placeName reg="Missouri" key="tgn,7007523" authname="tgn,7007523">Missouri</placeName>.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="857" />The resolution was referred to a committee of <num value="7">seven</num>. </p> </div3> 
<div3 type="letter" n="8" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head>Effect of the <q direct="unspecified">"Sad and unfortunate News."</q></head> <opener> <dateline> <name type="name"><placeName key="tgn,7013920" n="1.000 1" reg="Fortress Monroe, Hampton, Virginia" authname="tgn,7013920">Fortress Monroe</placeName>,</name> <date value="07-24" authname="--07-24">July 24.</date> </dateline> </opener> 
<p rend="nobreak">

<milestone unit="sentence" n="858" /> --The important movement expected to be made at <placeName reg="Old Point, Dare, North Carolina" key="tgn,2557597" authname="tgn,2557597">Old Point</placeName> has been postponed in consequence of the sad and unfortunate news of the defeat of the <rs>Federal</rs> troops, near <placeName key="tgn,2112877" n="1.000 541" reg="manassas, manassas, virginia" authname="tgn,2112877">Manassas</placeName>, on <dateStruct full="yes"><day type="name" full="yes">Sunday</day></dateStruct>. </p> </div3> 
<div3 type="letter" n="9" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head><persName n="Lincoln,,,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00600" reg="mostcommon:Lincoln,nomatch:0" authname="lincoln"><surname full="yes">Lincoln</surname></persName>'s <q direct="unspecified">"Effective Blockade."</q></head> <opener> <dateline> <name type="place"><placeName key="tgn,7013920" n="1.000 1" reg="Fortress Monroe, Hampton, Virginia" authname="tgn,7013920">Fortress Monroe</placeName>,</name> <date value="07-24" authname="--07-24">July 24.</date> </dateline> </opener> 
<p rend="nobreak">

<milestone unit="sentence" n="859" /> --A schooner from <placeName reg="Norfolk, Norfolk, Virginia" key="tgn,7014231" authname="tgn,7014231">Norfolk</placeName>, heavily laden, and probably with cannon, bound for <placeName reg="Richmond, Richmond, Virginia" key="tgn,7013964" authname="tgn,7013964">Richmond</placeName>, has run the blockade at <orgName n="Newport News" type="newspaper">Newport News</orgName> and got up safely into <placeName reg="Richmond, Richmond, Virginia" key="tgn,7013964" authname="tgn,7013964">James river</placeName>.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="860" />Only <num value="6">six</num> shots were fired at her. </p> </div3> 
<div3 type="letter" n="10" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head><persName n="Breckinridge,Mister,,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00601" reg="mostcommon:Breckinridge,nomatch:0" authname="breckinridge"><roleName n="Mister" full="yes">Mr.</roleName> <surname full="yes">Breckinridge</surname></persName>--another report.</head> <opener> <dateline> <name type="place">Washington,</name> <date value="07-23" authname="--07-23">July 23.</date> </dateline> </opener> 
<p rend="nobreak">

<milestone unit="sentence" n="861" /> --<persName n="Breckinridge,Mister,,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00602" reg="mostcommon:Breckinridge,nomatch:0" authname="breckinridge"><roleName n="Mister" full="yes">Mr.</roleName> <surname full="yes">Breckinridge</surname></persName> visited the <rs>Confederate</rs> prisoners here to-day, and offered them his sympathies. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="862" /> It is reported here that <persName n="Lee,General,,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00603" reg="mostcommon:Lee,nomatch:0" authname="lee"><roleName n="General" full="yes">Gen.</roleName> <surname full="yes">Lee</surname></persName> has gone to <placeName reg="Lynchburg, Lynchburg, Virginia" key="tgn,7013981" authname="tgn,7013981">Lynchburg</placeName> to intercept <persName n="McClellan,General,,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00604" reg="nearbymention:McClellan,George,B.,," authname="mcclellan,george,b."><roleName n="General" full="yes">Gen.</roleName> <surname full="yes">McClellan</surname></persName>. </p> </div3> 
<div3 type="letter" n="11" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head><orgName n="Northern Congress" type="congress">Northern Congress</orgName>.</head> <opener> <dateline> <name type="place">Washington,</name> <date value="07-24" authname="--07-24">July 24.</date> </dateline> </opener> 
<p rend="nobreak">

<milestone unit="sentence" n="863" /> --In the <rs type="place">House</rs> a bill was passed, leaving it to the <rs>President</rs>'s option to appoint Consuls at any foreign port to prevent piracy.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="864" />The Senate bill to accept <num value="500000">500,000</num> volunteers was passed. </p> </div3> 
<div3 type="letter" n="12" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head><persName n="Greeley,,,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00605" reg="mostcommon:Greeley,nomatch:0" authname="greeley"><surname full="yes">Greeley</surname></persName> down on the <rs>Cabinet</rs>.</head> <opener> <dateline> <name type="place">Louisville, Ky.,</name> <date value="07-25" authname="--07-25">July 25.</date> </dateline> </opener> 
<p rend="nobreak">

<milestone unit="sentence" n="865" /> --The Cincinnati papers contain the <orgName n="New York Tribune" type="newspaper">N. Y. Tribune's</orgName> call for the resignation of the <rs>Federal Cabinet</rs>, in consequence of their incompetency. </p> </div3> 
<div3 type="letter" n="13" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head>The best Joke of the <name>Season</name>.</head> <opener> <dateline> <name type="place">Washington</name> <date value="07-25" authname="--07-25">July 25.</date> </dateline> </opener> 
<p rend="nobreak">

<milestone unit="sentence" n="866" /> --There is no doubt the reason why the <rs>Confederates</rs> declined pursuing the retreating Federal forces was, that a panic occurred among them and they retreated to their <placeName key="tgn,2112877" n="1.000 541" reg="manassas, manassas, virginia" authname="tgn,2112877">Manassas</placeName> entrenchments!! </p> </div3> 
<div3 type="letter" n="14" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head>Pending duel.</head> <opener> <dateline> <name type="place">Washington</name> <date value="07-24" authname="--07-24">July 24.</date> </dateline> </opener> 
<p rend="nobreak">

<milestone unit="sentence" n="867" /> --A duel is pending here between <persName n="Burnett,Mister,,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00606" reg="mostcommon:Burnett,nomatch:0" authname="burnett"><roleName n="Mister" full="yes">Messrs.</roleName> <surname full="yes">Burnett</surname></persName> and <persName n="Richardson,Mister,,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00607" reg="nearbymention:Richardson,William,A.,," authname="richardson,william,a."><roleName n="Mister" full="yes" /><surname full="yes">Richardson</surname>.</persName> Friends are trying to effect an honorable adjustment. </p> </div3> 
<div3 type="letter" n="15" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head>A report Reaches <placeName reg="Washington, District of Columbia, United States" key="tgn,7013962" authname="tgn,7013962">Washington</placeName>.</head> <opener> <dateline> <name type="place">Washington,</name> <date value="07-24" authname="--07-24">July 24.</date> </dateline> </opener> 
<p rend="nobreak">

<milestone unit="sentence" n="868" /> --<persName n="Wadsworth,General,,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00608" reg="nearbymention:Wadsworth,John,S.,," authname="wadsworth,john,s."><roleName n="General" full="yes">Gen.</roleName><surname full="yes">Wadsworth</surname></persName> has just arrived from <placeName reg="Fairfax Court-House">Fairfax Court-House</placeName>, and reports that the <orgName n="Confederate Army" type="org">Confederate Army</orgName> is coming on. </p> </div3> 
<div3 type="letter" n="16" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head>On to <placeName reg="Alexandria, Alexandria, Virginia" key="tgn,7013269" authname="tgn,7013269">Alexandria</placeName>.</head> <opener> <dateline> <name type="place">Washington,</name> <date value="07-24" authname="--07-24">July 24.</date> </dateline> </opener> 
<p rend="nobreak">

<milestone unit="sentence" n="869" /> --The Confederate pickets extend to <placeName key="tgn,2111722" n="1.000 6" reg="falls church, falls church, virginia" authname="tgn,2111722">Fall's Church</placeName>.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="870" />[This is about <placeName><distance reg="4miles" full="yes" exact="U">four miles</distance> from <placeName reg="Alexandria, Alexandria, Virginia" key="tgn,7013269" authname="tgn,7013269">Alexandria, Va.</placeName></placeName>] </p> </div3> </div2> 
